<statement>
<p>Solve the equation: <m>\displaystyle{4}{\left({10}^{{{8}{x}}}\right)}-{10}={0}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=</m><input type="text" style="width:8.2ch" name="qn0" id="qn0" value="" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Question 1" class="text"/> </p>
<p>Round to 3 decimal places.</p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>0.05</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{4}{\left({10}^{{{8}{x}}}\right)}-{10}={0}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{4}{\left({10}^{{{8}{x}}}\right)}=-{10}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{10}^{{{8}{x}}}=-\frac{{10}}{{4}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{8}{x}={\log{{\left(-\frac{{10}}{{4}}\right)}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=\frac{{\log{{\left(-\frac{{10}}{{4}}\right)}}}}{{8}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}\approx{0.05}</m></p>
</solution>
</myopenmath>